  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "This is a skateboarding game very similar in gameplay to Tony Hawk's Pro Skater. You pick a skater and go through different skate parks, selecting either pro or amateur settings. You can also create your own skate park. Multiplayer competition is also provded, including 4 player serial play. Street Sk8er 2's sound track contains music from many well known bands such as Deftones, Ministry, and Static X.",
